==Standings==
{{2026 FIFA World Cup group tables|Group D}}

In the [[2026 FIFA World Cup knockout stage#Round of 32|round of 32]]:<ref name="regulations"/>
* The winner of Group D will advance to play the third-placed team of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group B|Group B]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group E|Group E]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group F|Group F]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group I|Group I]], or [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group J|Group J]].
* The runner-up of Group D will advance to play the runner-up of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group G|Group G]].
* The third-placed team of Group D might advance to play the winner of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group E|Group E]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group I|Group I]], or [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group K|Group K]] (if one of the [[2026 FIFA World Cup#Ranking of third-placed teams|eight best third-placed teams]] from the group stage).

